International shipping to Belize

Question
March 21, 2017

My daughter lives in Belize.  I wanted to send her something really nice for her birthday, a set of bamboo sheets would be perfect.  My problem, if I have you send them to me, I will then have to ship them, and it will take forever.  Do you do international shipping?
 


Thomas LeeAnswerAnswerDear Susan,
 Unfortunately we do not ship outside of the US. You can of course have your order shipped to you and then send them on .
thank you for your interest in Thomas Lee.
Tom M 






