Lee M. Thomas




 









Former Chairman and Chief Executive Officer – Rayonier
A director since 2011, Mr. Thomas is former chairman and CEO of Rayonier. He previously served as president and COO of Georgia-Pacific Corp. Prior to Georgia Pacific, he was chairman of Law Companies Environmental Group Inc., and administrator of the U.S. Environmental Protection Agency. Mr. Thomas also serves on the boards of Airgas Inc., the Regal Entertainment Group and the World Resource Institute.  Mr. Thomas serves on the Environmental Policy & Safety, Human Resources & Compensation, and Science & Technology committees for the Board.
8/15

