Machine washable

Sizing:

Queen set includes one flat sheet measuring 110 inches in length by 96 inches in width, one fitted sheet measuring 80 inches in length by 60 inches in width with a 18 inch pocket and two standard pillowcases, each measuring 34 inches in length by 20 inches in width
King set includes one flat sheet measuring 114 inches length by 113 inches in width, one fitted sheet measuring 80 inches in length by 78 inches in width with a 18 inch pocket and two king pillowcases, each measuring 32 inches in length by 20 inches in width
Cal King set includes one flat sheet measuring 114 inches in length by 113 inches in width, one fitted sheet measuring 84 inches in length by 72 inches in width with a 18 inch pockets and two pillowcases, each measuring 42 inches in length by 20 inches in width

